    <item>
      <title>私人信贷将继续增长：Antares 的 Mathew</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/private-credit-will-continue-to-grow-antares-mathew-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去几年，私人信贷市场处于黄金时代，Antares Capital Advisers 总裁 Vivek Mathew 表示，市场规模比大多数人想象的要大，而且将继续增长。他在“彭博市场”节目中与 Lisa Abramowicz 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/private-credit-will-continue-to-grow-antares-mathew-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:17:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
